cs.ET, cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.SE, cs.CR

The paper deals with the verification of quantum circuits, which falls under the category of formal methods and verification (cs.ET). The paper also presents a verified compiler, which involves programming language theory (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). The verification methods involve logical reasoning (cs.LO) and the potential for errors in the circuit design falls under cryptography and security (cs.CR).
